ful+learning%22&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=IBo6GMysV6&amp;sig=CjaivsVuLUaBhpDD5QQK6VV61t4&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=0ZeoVIbtD9eJuASxg4KQCQ&amp;ved=0CEoQ6AEwCDgU#v=onepage&amp;q=research%20%2B%20%22artful%20learning%22&amp;f=false\">https://books.google.co.in/books?id=iakFqWZGvhkC&amp;pg=PA1059&amp;lpg=PA1059&amp;dq=research+%2B+%22artful+learning%22&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=IBo6GMysV6&amp;sig=CjaivsVuLUaBhpDD5QQK6VV61t4&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=0ZeoVIbtD9eJuASxg4KQCQ&amp;ved=0CEoQ6AEwCDgU#v=onepage&amp;q=research%20%2B%20%22artful%20learning%22&amp;f=false</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.indiana.edu/~bcec/events/RFKS/RFKS2011/artful.html\">\"Artful Learning\"</a>. <i>indiana.edu</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2011-01-12</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=indiana.edu&amp;rft.atitle=Artful+Learning&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiana.edu%2F~bcec%2Fevents%2FRFKS%2FRFKS2011%2Fartful.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AArtful+Learning\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Artful_Learning&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Further reading\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.safaribooksonline.com/library/view/andragogical-and-pedagogical/9781466658721/978-1-4666-5872-1.ch015.xhtml\">Artful Learning: Holistic Curriculum Development for Mind, Body, 